message.body: Hey sweets. What are you up to tonight? I've had a weird day and could use some release... That's a come on.
Boner. Unfortunately I'm at saman's cabin right now! :( what was up with your day, baby?
Ugh there was this huge tragic fire in new ulm and Megan got in a car accident, she's totally fine though, and Justin is disappointing. And im making it all about me. Hah. I just feel out of sorts.
Oh no!!! That's a lot of crazy shit though... I wish I were there to feed you wine
I'm doing ok with that myself. Don't worry about THAT
Haha, atta girl. Let's hang as soon as I get back?
I'm going to photogs house so if I'm disemboweled that's where you'll find me
That is the most alarming text I've ever received
Have fun sweetie. Think happy thoughts ;)
NOT disemboweled but practically. Think that's the last time I'll be Seeing him as he proceeded to show me his life's work on his iPad afterwards....
